(secondQuint)Reveal LINQ In-Office 2 (RIO 2) Study International.

 The traditional location of the LINQ cent insertion procedure is the catheterization laboratory, electrophysiology laboratory, or operating room.

 The purpose of the RIO 2 International study is to provide clinical and economic evidence to support moving the LINQ cent insertion procedure outside these traditional locations within the hospital, referred to as "out-of-cathlab".

